ary|Judiciary]] (Chairman: [[Charles A. Culberson]]) \n* [[United States Senate Committee on the Library|Library]] (Chairman: [[Luke Lea (American politician, born 1879)|Luke Lea]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Manufactures|Manufactures]] (Chairman: [[James A. Reed]]) \n* [[United States Senate Committee on Military Affairs|Military Affairs]] (Chairman: [[George E. Chamberlain]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Mines and Mining|Mines and Mining]] (Chairman: [[Thomas J. Walsh]])\n* [[United States Senate Select Committee on the Mississippi River and its Tributaries|Mississippi River and its Tributaries]] (Select) (Chairman: [[Albert B. Cummins]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on National Banks|National Banks]] (Chairman: [[Charles F. Johnson]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Naval Affairs|Naval Affairs]] (Chairman: [[Benjamin R. Tillman]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Pacific Islands and Puerto Rico|Pacific Islands and Puerto Rico]] (Chairman: [[John F. Shafroth]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Pacific Railroads|Pacific Railroads]] (Chairman: [[Frank B. Brandegee]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Patents|Patents]] (Chairman: [[Ollie M. James]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Pensions|Pensions]] (Chairman: [[Benjamin F. Shively]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on the Philippines|Philippines]] (Chairman: [[Gilbert M. Hitchcock]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Post Office and Post Roads|Post Office and Post Roads]] (Chairman: [[John H. Bankhead]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Printing|Printing]] (Chairman: [[Duncan U. Fletcher]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Private Land Claims|Private Land Claims]] (Chairman: [[Henry Cabot Lodge]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Privileges and Elections|Privileges and Elections]] (Chairman: [[John W. Kern]])\n* [[United States Senate Committee on Public Buildings and Grounds|Public Buildings and Grounds]] (Chairman: [[Claude A. 